Key Match Events: Orlando Arcia hit a pair of solo homers, the first one as part of back-to-back shots with Sean Murphy in the third inning.
Sean Murphy also hit a solo homer in the third inning.
Bryson Stott homered to right in the fourth inning.
Orlando Arcia hit another solo homer to center in the sixth inning.
Gio Urshela doubled to left, scoring Sean Murphy in the sixth inning.
Matt Olson doubled to center, scoring Marcell Ozuna in the seventh inning.
J.T. Realmuto homered to left center in the seventh inning.
